# ============================================================
# AST — Phase Portrait Visualization
# Plots the model's trajectory through activation space
# token by token, for one or more prompts.
#
# Run this as a separate Colab notebook.
# Requires the AST backend to be running with /sequence endpoint.
# ============================================================


